Class PropertyIdValueImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.wikidata.wdtk.datamodel.implementation.PropertyIdValueImpl
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    EntityIdValue, IriIdentifiedValue, PropertyIdValue, Value

    public class PropertyIdValueImpl
extends Object
implements PropertyIdValue
    Generic implementation of PropertyIdValue that works with arbitrary Wikibase instances: it requires a baseIri that identifies the site globally.

    Markus Kroetzsch
